<plot>In a town where everyone has a point, Obleo is born round-headed. He grows up as an outcast, wearing a hat to cover his deformation. The towns-folk become suspicious of Obleo, blaming him for their bad luck. The Evil Count and his son have him and his dog banished forever into the unknown regions of Pointless Forest. To the Counts great shame, Obleo returns to Arrow-town with the news that he doesn't have to have a pointed head to have meaning.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?583157</url></doc>
